	* utils/kannel-log-summary: Wrote. Requires AWK. Improvements
	welcome.

Tue Apr  4 14:57:55 2000  Lars Wirzenius  <liw@wapit.com>

	* gw/urltrans.c: Changed to use List.

Tue Apr  4 14:42:54 2000  Lars Wirzenius  <liw@wapit.com>

