	timers (This is,  how ever, still commented out. It must be tested with
	a new version of fakewap.). Corrected some of memory leaks pointed out
	by Paul Keogh.

	* wtp.c: Added lock for the global wtp transaction identifier.

2000-03-27    <Kalle Marjola <rpr@wapit.com>>

