	check.

at Feb 26 16:57:40 CET 2000	Patrick Schaaf	<bof@bof.de>

	* gw/wsp_http.c, gw/wsp.h, gw/wapbox.c: added configuration
	options device-home and map-url; see gw/wapbox.wapconf for
